{"type": "article", "id": 24535, "title": "面包袋包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 129, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061608400heTuAROq7MWHwaP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组装面包袋子的包装来自哥伦比亚平面设计 Siegenthaler &amp; Co，是为当地一家老的面包品牌 MASA 重新设计的。他们将面包本身的黑白照片放到了包装袋上，使得在大街上也能拥有吸引力，似乎透过了图片看到了里面松软可口的面包。此外，每组包装除了黑、白色外都会使用一种彩色，都是天蓝、橙黄这样清新而活泼的颜色，保持了简洁干净和年轻的特征。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160836MkaUcnxRITJHGZBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616083758NwJyuKpZE0GMqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061608384qeTPd0D23K8mFr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 260px; width: 375px; left: 470px; top: 1041px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160839tWpBFlZh1wbdmGui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160839OiAHlQZD0sgeB6C2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061608406YCNd9nv30smJpEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}